name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Google UDM 14 Web search mode (no AI)

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds the &udm=14 parameter to every Google search to set 'Web' as the default search mode (without AI and other clutter)

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
OK Google, Just Show Me The Search Results

Adds the &udm=14 parameter to every Google search to set 'Web' as the default search mode (without AI and other clutter)
